# Generate Excel — Business Logic

## Output Format
- Sheet name: `Opening SO`
- 109 columns (A–DE) defined in `OUTPUT_COLUMNS`
- Each column has an Excel letter comment (e.g. `# A`, `# BH`)

## SAP Report Column Index Mapping
Key SAP columns referenced by index (0-based):
- 0: Sales Order No, 2: Material No, 7: Payment Term Code
- 9: Sold To No, 11: Ship To No, 13: Shipping Label
- 15: Sales Employee Name, 16: PO Number, 17: Plant
- 20: SO Date, 21: PO Date, 22: Request Delivery Date
- 23: Order Quantity, 24: Sales Unit, 34: Amount (AI)
- 40: ZP01 flag (AO), 42: ZP01 Amount (AQ), 46: ZP01 Value (AU)
- 48: ZC01 flag (AW), 50: ZC01 Amount (AY), 54: ZC01 Value (BC)
- 56: ZD13 flag (BE), 62: ZD13 Value (BK)

## Lookup Logic (MySQL tables)
| Output Column | SAP Source | Lookup |
|---|---|---|
| Customer (D/E) | sold_to_no | `customer_master.old_code` → internal_id |
| Ship to Customer (F/G) | ship_to_no | `customer_master.old_code` → internal_id |
| Shipping Label (H) | Shipping label col | Fuzzy match → `shipping_label_master.address_label` (≥80%) |
| Payment Terms (N/O) | payment_term_code | `payment_term_master.payment_term_code` |
| Sales Ref (AD/AE) | Sales employee name | Fuzzy match → `sales_rep_master.first_name_th+last_name_th` (≥80%) |
| Item (AZ/BA) | Material No | `item_master.old_item_code` |
| Location (BB/BC) | Plant | `location_master.plant` |

## SAP Number Format
Values like `"  0.560000000-"` use `parse_sap_number()` — handles trailing minus sign.

## Calculated Columns
- BH = SAP AI (Amount via parse_sap_number)
- BI = BD × BH
- BJ = BH + (SAP AQ + SAP AY)  ← ZP01 + ZC01 amounts
- BK = BJ × BD
- BL = 'VAT_TH:VAT 7%', BM = BK × 7%, BN = BK + BM
- BY = sum(CB,CE,CH,CK,CN,CQ), DA = sum(CT,CW,CZ)

## Inserted Rows
1. **Subtotal rows** (green `#C6EFCE`): One per SO with promotions. Item=-2, Item='Subtotal'. Sums discount/promo columns across SO.
2. **Promotion row 1** (pink `#FCE4EC`): Below subtotal if CT≠0. Item=72795, Item='LDCD-IR-001'. BI/BK=CT, tax calculated.

## Hardcoded Constants
Product=CZ, Domestic, Subsidiary=2/Double A (1991) PLC, Incoterms=5/DAP, Currency=THB, ExRate=1, Country=324/Thailand, Continent=2/Asia
